<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="continue-v">continue <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'tɪnjuː/    美 /kən'tɪnjuː/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>继续；持续；延续：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I hope that this kind of activity will continue in the future.
我希望这种活动今后能继续办下去。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children asked the old man to <strong>continue with</strong> his story.
孩子们让老人继续讲故事。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Babbage continued his work in London for four years.
巴比奇继续在伦敦工作了四年。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>continue doing sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Though wounded, they continued fighting.
虽然负了伤，但他们仍然坚持战斗。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>continue to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She continued to work after her long vacation.
长假过后她又继续工作了。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>维持…的情况：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The winter continued (to be) cold and wet.
冬天依旧寒冷、潮湿。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She continues in good health.
她身体依然很好。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="to-be-continued">to be continued</h3>
<p>1.<strong>未完待续</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>continued /kən'tɪnjuːd/ adj [只用于名词前]  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>continued / continuing effort
不断的努力</p></div>

<h2 id="_4">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The rain c<strong><em>_</em></strong>_ for days, so we could not go out to play.  （2005 浙江）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. continued  </p></div>